# Normalise text files to LF in the repository; check out native on each platform.
* text=auto

# Keep these explicitly LF even in the working tree (shell scripts / yaml / sql).
*.sh   text eol=lf
*.yml  text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.sql  text eol=lf
*.bicep text eol=lf

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GOLDEN TELEMETRY FIXTURES — byte-exact engine output. NEVER convert line
# endings: the Idempotency-Key is a SHA-256 over the exact batch bytes
# (lines joined by '\n'), so a CRLF conversion would change the hash and break
# the ContractParityTests on checkout/CI. Treat as binary (no eol conversion).
# This rule is LAST so it wins over `* text=auto`.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
tests/Vouchfx.Telemetry.Backend.UnitTests/Fixtures/** -text
